{"tid":489420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰隆尼亞選舉獨派恐失過半優勢","createTime":"2017-12-04T16:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T07:46:07.000Z","uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"421e74faf4163c2d6a15697994e712bbb93511e0","tid":489420,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"（中央社馬德里4日綜合外電報導）根據西班牙公共研究機構「社會研究中心」今天公布的官方民意調查結果，支持獨立的加泰隆尼亞政黨預期將在21日的地方選舉中失去議會過半數優勢。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，社會研究中心（Sociological Research Centre）進行的民調結果顯示，支持獨立的「全力為加泰隆尼亞」聯盟（Junts per Catalunya）預料將在地方議會選舉贏得25至26席，「加泰隆尼亞左翼共和黨」（ERC）取得32席，而極左派「人民團結候選人黨」（CUP）獲得9席。<br />\n<br />\n這使得支持加泰隆尼亞獨立的政黨陣營在共有135席的地方議會中只能取得67席，失去之前的勉強過半優勢。<br />\n<br />\n民調顯示，西班牙執政黨人民黨（People's Party）可能在加泰隆尼亞議會只贏得7席，社會勞工黨（Socialists）拿下21席，親商的公民黨（Ciudadanos）取得31至32席，西班牙反撙節政黨「我們可以」（Podemos）的分支「加泰隆尼亞一同-我們可以」（CatComu-Podem）則能贏得9席。（譯者：中央社張正芊）1061204<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201712040346.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201712040346.aspx&d=ccqcd2TaKq5pbInitvPWXG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c5f6ed37\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201712040346.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"4d6a23392a312f1bcf83b1858577f3d4dfb0a047","tid":489420,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"睇跣，好多五毛會入嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fabae6427ce0d4847c1af17275c02d611f11f25","tid":489420,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gi